spec_data.Name: texlive-enctex
spec_data.Description:
EncTeX is (another) TeX extension, written at the change-file
level. It provides means of translating input on the way into
TeX. It allows, for example, translation of multibyte
sequences, such as utf-8 encoding.
spec_data.Signature: RSA/SHA256, Sun 06 Aug 2017 08:20:00 AM EDT, Key ID f55e7430f5282ee4
spec_data.Summary: A TeX extension that translates input on its way into TeX
